{"tid":1910913,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"腥港人vs真正港人分別","createTime":"2020-03-05T03:54:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-05T11:34:13.000Z","uid":205525,"like":42,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"31302fcceed94d782fe0b712c4a5458bb2f7a6c6","tid":1910913,"uid":205525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:54:16.000Z","msg":"由細到大，小弟我都未返過鄉下亦都唔知係邊<br />\n中學小學個陣成日見啲同學返鄉下逗利是逗到成萬蚊返黎 我都有少少羨慕 <br />\n<br />\n但到依家睇返覺得佢地會返去既都係大陸人，純粹係佢地老豆老母係早十幾年前先落黎香港(帶頭盔先唔好話我咩咩祖先都係大陸落黎)點都有有少少大陸feel<br />\n<br />\n人生返過兩次支那<br />\n第一次係bb仔<br />\n第二次係中學要習訓，老豆老母差啲唔比我去<br />\n驚啲大陸人唔知會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n各位巴打點睇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />留係香港<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />傳統啊"},{"pid":"dd552a82dcdad564e4a208c9b030bbde1579471d","tid":1910913,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:59:32.000Z","msg":"你用得個返字，證明你都未完全擺脫支那人思想"},{"pid":"0a522e6456c315a73af4fc1c7d8d2fc7bef2a6a1","tid":1910913,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:00:43.000Z","msg":"淨係比垃撚圾中學迫去過一次 屌你老母真係第三世界咁款"},{"pid":"78ddb16a1498edf668e35e5f02b5af0a47e5ef96","tid":1910913,"uid":15195,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:03:21.000Z","msg":"你做過啲咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n分到咁細緻有咩意思"},{"pid":"2a09e0a8d28daa8e2591d3021b3748dfc6dcd780","tid":1910913,"uid":205525,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"dd552a82dcdad564e4a208c9b030bbde1579471d","tid":1910913,"uid":196924,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T03:59:32.000Z","msg":"你用得個返字，證明你都未完全擺脫支那人思想"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T04:03:35.000Z","msg":"咁應該要用咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1217df37713cccf028b7066b275e56678a76330","tid":1910913,"uid":205525,"like":